bilingual.source: She loves to learn about foreign cultures.
bilingual.target: 她喜欢了解外国的文化。

bilingual.source: The company imports foreign goods for resale.
bilingual.target: 这家公司进口外国的商品进行转售。

bilingual.source: He is studying foreign languages at university.
bilingual.target: 他在大学学习外国的语言。

bilingual.source: She enjoys watching foreign films in her free time.
bilingual.target: 她喜欢在空闲时间观看外国的电影。

bilingual.source: She enjoys the expat lifestyle in a foreign country.
bilingual.target: 她喜欢在外国的外籍人士生活方式。

bilingual.source: They hired a foreign consultant to help with the project.
bilingual.target: 他们雇佣了一位外国的顾问来帮助这个项目。

bilingual.source: This book introduces many cultures from foreign countries.
bilingual.target: 这本书介绍了许多外国的文化。

bilingual.source: He always worships things foreign and fawns on foreign countries, thinking that foreign things are better than domestic ones.
bilingual.target: 他总是崇洋媚外，认为外国的东西都比本国的好。
我们应该庆祝外国的节日吗？

bilingual.source: They see my foreign face and instantly mute.
bilingual.target: 他看到我的脸是外国的和立即装聋作哑.

list.abstract: foreign，英语单词，主要用作形容词，作形容词的意思是“外国的；外交的；异质的；不相关的”。

演唱：Bohaan Phoneix，Howie Lee

yingyinNormal.en: Familiar can turn foreign on a dime.
yingyinNormal.zh: 熟悉和陌生只有一线之隔。

yingyinNormal.en: It may not be as foreign as you think.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它也许并没有你想象的那么不同。

yingyinNormal.en: I was an outsider in a foreign land. A freak.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一个人背井离乡，像个怪胎。

yingyinNormal.en: You can't let the campaign drive our foreign policy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不能让竞选决定外交政策。

yingyinNormal.en: Who's Cathy spoken to? Foreign Minister hasn't returned her call.
yingyinNormal.zh: 凯茜给谁打电话呢？外交部长仍未回电话。

yingyinNormal.en: If I don't win in Iowa, there is no foreign policy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我拿不下爱荷华，就没什么外交政策可言了。

yingyinNormal.en: Fear of foreign competition once led countries to try and produce everything they needed and impose heavy taxes to keep out foreign goods.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对外国竞争感到的恐惧让一些国家决定自给自足，自行生产所有产品，并且向国外的商品收相当重的税。

yingyinNormal.en: But the next time you hear a foreign language, pay attention.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过当你下一次听到一门外语的时候，留意一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Six years ago you held the brief for Foreign Operations, code name Love.
yingyinNormal.zh: 六年前你负责海外行动，代号为爱。

yingyinNormal.en: You know we were away, In a foreign, romantic country. I blame London. Bad London.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道，我们人在国外，又是浪漫的异乡。都怪伦敦不好。坏伦敦。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, no need to be nervous with me. I'm just a harmless giant from a foreign land.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你无需对我紧张，我只是一个来自异国，人畜无害的巨人。

yingyinNormal.en: 17 years and still evolving with the times remains an entirely foreign concept to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 十七年都过去了，你仍然不打算与时代同步。

yingyinNormal.en: No matter the policy question, foreign or domestic, we hammer Dunbar's lack of experience.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不论是政策，国际或国内问题，我们都抨击邓巴经验不足。

yingyinNormal.en: Then we grew stagnant. Foreign competitors began producing steel that was better and cheaper.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后便停滞了，外国公司开始产钢，比我们的更好更便宜。

yingyinNormal.en: Now let's look at where we are in reality, recent headlines, in the media, include Foreign Policy magazine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那现在来看看，现实中我们的情况，媒体中最近的标题，包括外交政策杂志。

yingyinNormal.en: I think she slept at a friend's house. What friend? Not a normal name, starts with a vowel, possibly foreign.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得她好像去朋友家过夜了。什么朋友？不是个常见的名字，是元音开头的，很可能是个外国人。

yingyinNormal.en: Manufacturing has grown. Our deficits have shrunk. Our dependence on foreign oil is down. Clean energy is up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 制造业在蓬勃发展，我们的赤字已经削减了，我们对国外石油的依赖在下降，清洁能源在发展。

yingyinNormal.en: I've identified the host as general Zod of Kandor. Acknowledging presence of foreign genetic material. Analyzing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 已辨认出基因主人为坎多城的佐德将军。正在确认外来基因物质。正在分析。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll have Secretary Durant work with your foreign minister, and then we'll take it from there. Are you open to that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会让国务卿杜兰特跟你的外交部长接洽，然后我们再谈，这样可以吗？

yingyinNormal.en: In 221 BC, the first emperor of China decided to stop the constant conflict by uniting the country against foreign invaders.
yingyinNormal.zh: 公元前221年，秦始皇决定抛弃矛盾，上下一心，以御外敌。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: A recent study attempts to separate them by looking at bribery prosecutions under America's <highlight>Foreign</highlight> Corrupt Practices Act.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最近的一项研究试图通过研究美国《反海外腐败法》下的贿赂起诉来区分它们。

examination_example.sentence: The report also advocates greater study of <highlight>foreign</highlight> languages, international affairs and the expansion of study abroad programs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该报告还提倡更多地学习外语、国际事务和扩大留学项目。

sense_info_list.en: dealing with or relating to other countries

examination_example.sentence: The State, War, and Navy Building housed the three Executive Branch Departments most intimately associated with formulating and conducting the nation's <highlight>foreign</highlight> policy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 国家、战争和海军大楼是与制定和执行国家外交政策最密切相关的三个行政部门的所在地。
